 not rejected","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"March 29, 2014","format":false,"excerpt":"Anas ibn Malik reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cSupplication is not rejected between the call to prayer and its commencement.\u201d They said, \"What should we say, O Messenger of Allah?\" The Prophet said, \"Ask Allah for wellness in the world and in the\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":5660,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/08\/29\/supplication-in-witr-prayer\/","url_meta":{"origin":32803,"position":1},"title":"Hadith on Witr: The Prophet\u2019s supplication in Witr prayer","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"August 29, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Ubayy ibn Ka\u2019b reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, when he finished his Witr prayer with invocations of peace, he would say, \u201cGlory to the King, the Holy.\u201d Source: Sunan Abi\u0304 Da\u0304wu\u0304d 1430 Grade:\u00a0Sahih\u00a0(authentic) according to Al-Albani \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0623\u064f\u0628\u064e\u064a\u0650\u0651 \u0628\u0652\u0646\u0650 \u0643\u064e\u0639\u0652\u0628\u064d \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0643\u064e\u0627\u0646\u064e \u0631\u064e\u0633\u064f\u0648\u0644\u064f \u0627\u0644\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0647\u0650\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":33279,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/08\/21\/no-dua-is-better\/","url_meta":{"origin":32803,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Dua: No request better than for wellness in world, Hereafter","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"August 21, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cNo supplication a servant can say is better than this: O Allah, I ask You for wellness in the world and in the Hereafter.\u201d Source: Sunan Ibn Ma\u0304jah 3851 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Albani \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":34448,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2020\/10\/05\/dua-between-adhan-iqamah\/","url_meta":{"origin":32803,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Adhan: Dua not rejected between Adhan and Iqamah","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"October 5, 2020","format":false,"excerpt":"Anas ibn Malik reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cWhen the call to prayer is announced, the gates of heaven are opened and the supplication is answered. The supplication between the call to prayer and the commencement is never turned back.\u201d Source: al-Du\u2019a\u0304\u2019 li-T\u0323abara\u0304ni\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":25705,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2017\/12\/29\/two-dua-seldom-rejected\/","url_meta":{"origin":32803,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Dua: Two supplications rarely turned away","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"December 29, 2017","format":false,"excerpt":"Sahl ibn Sa\u2019d reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cTwo supplications are not rejected, or seldom rejected: the supplication at the call to prayer and at the time of the rain.\u201d Source: Sunan Abi\u0304 Da\u0304wu\u0304d 2540 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Albani \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0633\u064e\u0647\u0652\u0644\u0650\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":23208,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2016\/06\/14\/dua-oppressed-ascends-heaven\/","url_meta":{"origin":32803,"position":5},"title":"Hadith on Dua: Supplication of oppressed ascends to heaven","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"June 14, 2016","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibn Umar reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cBeware of the supplication of the oppressed, for it ascends to the heavens as if it were a flare.\u201d Source: al-Mustadrak \u2018ala\u0301 al-S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323ayn 81 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Albani \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0650 \u0627\u0628\u0652\u0646\u0650 \u0639\u064f\u0645\u064e\u0631\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0631\u064e\u0633\u064f\u0648\u0644\u064f\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]}],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dail